# Claude Code per-machine config (settings.local.json, worktrees, etc.).
# Use .claude/* (with star) so the directory itself stays traversable —
# git can't re-include children if the parent directory is excluded.
.claude/*
# DO track the memory subfolder — these are project context notes that
# should sync across machines via git so future Claude sessions (on any
# computer) read the same priors.
!.claude/memory/
!.claude/memory/**
